name: T-DOGE
description: T-DOGE BlockChain is a public chain based on the underlying technology of the blockchain. Through a decentralized structure, the real economy is connected to the blockchain to create an application ecology. T-DOGE is committed to empowering the transformation and upgrading of the real economy and providing top-level business model design for entities , Token economic model design, corporate commercial value reshaping, blockchain technology development and scenario application and other overall chain reform services, realize corporate value interconnection, and build a new economic ecology with consensus and trust.
